              "body": {
                "type": "TextualBody",
                "value": "O — Observation: The Edukit systems image is repeated here within a spread containing earlier documentary material explicitly concerned with links, two-way communication, specialist connection and group organisation. C — Comparison: The juxtaposition invites comparison between the communications logic represented in the earlier material and the Edukit systems image. H — Hypothesis: Edukit may represent a rescaling of an earlier communications logic from facility to planetary system.",
